{"tid":1290924,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊設計新政黨logo","createTime":"2019-07-06T16:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T16:22:54.000Z","uid":275176,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c88fb4e0594f6133dcc6afe63613f172a8ef71fc","tid":1290924,"uid":275176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:13:17.000Z","msg":"我地個新組織Descendants of Victoria City黎緊會係英國註冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Descendants-of-Victoria-City-2267996923412983/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDescendants-of-Victoria-City-2267996923412983%2F&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zc3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=2b6b76d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Descendants-of-Victoria-City-2267996923412983/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主要係會爭取bno權益同繼承權<br />\n有興趣加入我地歡迎係fb聯絡<br />\n<br />\n仲有本身諗住同HKIP發起公投<br />\n不過好老實 反應未如理想<br />\n潑冷水係預期之內<br />\n<br />\n但我地相信要爭取民主自由<br />\n係要透過我地自己表達出嚟<br />\n一直未有普選<br />\n其中一個說詞係話香港未有呢個公民質素<br />\n通過公投就可以話俾全世界知香港人係值得擁有民主自由<br />\n<br />\n而家由大家決定想唔想要呢個公投<br />\n入去投個票<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/587351581323770/posts/2324516364273941/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F587351581323770%2Fposts%2F2324516364273941%2F&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zc3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=d39276f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/587351581323770/posts/2324516364273941/</a><br />\n<br />\n而家暫時未有黨徽<br />\n大家一齊幫手設計"},{"pid":"6e7b5513d9b2dcf2178cf5bdfdc590448c906367","tid":1290924,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de00bbd589f7c66a5673d994f38a6b632b9c20f9","tid":1290924,"uid":4917,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rs0chVa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRs0chVa.png&h=eb5e